The '''Sith Shadows''' were a group of thugs who were known to attack [[Force-sensitive/Legends|Force-sensitives]] during the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

==Characteristics==
[[File:SithShadowThug-TCGCOTF.jpg|thumb|left|180px|An armored Sith Shadow]]
They were generally seen on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]], near the village of [[Aurilia]], though were reportedly seen on other planets also. Though many species were Sith Shadows, [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] were never seen. The [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] [[Mellichae]] led the Shadows until imprisoned by the citizens of Aurilia.

The Sith Shadows may have engaged in regular thefts in the village of Aurilia: they were often found carrying valuable resources only used there. Those resources were often returned by spacers and used for much-needed repairs.

==Behind the scenes==
Sith Shadows appeared as non-player characters in the video game ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]'', a [[Star Wars video games#Massively multiplayer online role-playing game|massively multiplayer online role-playing game]] developed by [[Sony]] Online Entertainment and published by [[LucasArts]], prior to its closure on [[December 15]], [[2011]].

